## Skills First (CRITICAL)

Before doing anything manually, check if a skill or slash command exists for the task.
Skills encode workflow knowledge that manual steps will miss.

**If a skill exists, use it.** Do not attempt the task manually.
If a skill fails, stop and ask -- do NOT fall back to manual.

